Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时也不是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的梦想在闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把双眼闭上便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中的一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕 现在是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃 Step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓着梦想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常也和你一起向明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进 Step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想坚信着 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想向着天空大声呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧着 in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡,为了打倒支配着遥远星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又再一次成为救世主进行冒险旅程了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星界山的第一星界是有趣的童话世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里我们要找到能令花开的星之风吹起才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在喜杰喜杰镇中打倒了一半布其兄弟的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了要往星之风宫殿出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四话\N跳舞吧 牛之西班牙舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜拳,猜拳 输了的人要背人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀、石头、布!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是大叔输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是在下?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅真弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下这方面是很弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是身体很强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨,三盘两胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行,到下一个弯前也不会再猜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只到下一个弯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是下一个弯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去到哪里啊?在下不是马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对,不是马呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀,你不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河马,河马…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,终于来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让你得意下去了,让我教教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是跳舞的时候啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,露易·"人妖"大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对,是玛格西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打来得真是时候,竟看见我跳裙舞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你-真-坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥明!渡他们终于接近你的市镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗?不论怎样也不能让他们再前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这响板就没问题了 "久等了"大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是玛格西啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,有转弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜拳啊,猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,还是不要玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止是13和35败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下猜拳为什么会这么弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑道的话却是一流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为只是你太单纯吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单…单纯!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你应该说是纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,应该说是没有失去少年心的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯的大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么?在下怎么会是单纯啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,有钱掉在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,这里也没有花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗牛开始了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗牛开始了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗牛?去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?其他人全不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛…牛…牛之西班牙舞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…河马 到底怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来让他们受更多苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘飘攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,你带着师傅逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法,拉牛之术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫渡,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫美琪,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫火美子,还有我带着这只叫牛牛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!为什么在下是牛牛啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔变回河马了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是为什么会变成那样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…每当支配这市镇的肥明一跳起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些牛就不知为何会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么回事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大叔虽是河马却变成牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是河马!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要阻止她再令市民受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟控制着牛的心令市民受苦而高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救世主渡是不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来了呢\N小朋友,看在你份上我就停手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是求人做事时自己也要做些相应的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相应的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说 你要我做什么我就做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打倒了我的牛侍卫,我就听你的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好威风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哗!有很多牛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,我现在来了 你等我!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来,我从老婆婆那儿拿忍部道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,火美子呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是牛牛丸,我是牛牛丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位牛先生,这里有好好吃的草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先到先得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那算什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟可引开我的牛侍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次行不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰斯耳奇山,做好心理准备战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡的性命由我来取了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对,有为这时候而设的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神奇饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有增加攻击力的鲑鱼饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不知道哪个是鲑鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这么肮脏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以挑食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是酸梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位还记得吗?吃了酸梅饭团的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三分钟内智力会增加,也就是说头脑会变好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对那大肌肉的家伙增加智力有什么用啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等,反正我力量就不及它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可以用头脑决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有方法了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,你做它的对手一会吧 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣有趣…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛先生和我玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么字 是用mo字开头的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"已经"吗?那么"树木"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"桃树"厉害厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到牛先生出题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,可以了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗牛士渡,现在登场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哗!渡好有型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题:我是谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,现在看看幕后人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来,最初是这一位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜,是牛国的爱丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜,是义牛报恩 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龟牛赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是竹牛公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是牛雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是牛新娘报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小牛物语、野牛与我、三只小肥牛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了! 渡,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的河马也加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个了,是那个响板控制着牛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会把这响板交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘飘攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,我取到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了,可恶的渡,我不会就此算数的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,在下是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔果然是动物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,这次用魔神决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,渡 交给在下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战-神-丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂! 战神丸?对,立即来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要收拾你比借火容易,尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是胡说一通!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧,战神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛武一郎流,剑之舞!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用尾巴就足以收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了呢,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧,我做你对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招,牛扒飞弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你吃多点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心,这样的飞弹我处理给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是肉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把这么好的肉浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,牛舌飞弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,好货好货!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,龙神丸 再来一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在攻击是我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里?肥明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我用斗牛剑给你最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀!不可以动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"人妖"大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对,是玛格西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想吃沙拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡第一,火美子也了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很多谢你们,这样我们就可以和牛儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心地活下去了 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的市镇从以前起就以种植玫瑰而闻名的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题,我定会令玫瑰开给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美琪小姐,星之风宫殿在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星之风宫殿?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是,但听说在加拉查那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一座谁也不能接近的恐怖城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜杰喜杰镇的人说过是个很美丽的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也有去看一看的价值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那个加拉查在哪边?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨,小渡 不要用猜拳用点指兵兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,师傅 要赶快到加拉查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀、石头、布!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是在下?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?这个胸口在驱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop!已不能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也一个劲儿地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油门不用放开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直踏着 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:23:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是速度的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TONIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直望着的瞳孔涌上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜 MY LOVE

